history.content: Usually, such discrepancies mean either you are looking at different semesters or there has been a change in the data that just hasn't crossed over to update the parallel system. If the latter, that should be fixed a few times each day.

On course catalog, CS61C is scheduled for TUTH 11:00 am - 12:29 pm, however when I add it in schedule planner from Cal Central, it lists a time of MW 5:00pm - 6:29pm. Which is the correct time and can this please be updated across sites?
